  "texts": [
    "This configuration aims to improve both evidence coverage and ranking precision in multi-hop QA scenarios.",
    "We report dataset-specific evaluation metrics in accordance with the protocols defined for each benchmark.",
    "MultiHop-RAG.",
    "Following Tang and Yang (2024), we report the following three retrievaloriented metrics:",
    "• Hits@k for k ∈ {4, 10} which represents the percentage of questions for which at least one gold evidence appears in the top-k retrieved passages."
